{"tid":714911,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"世界盃16強隨時已經有幾場大戰，大牌球隊走埋同一邊","createTime":"2018-06-24T04:29:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T08:40:09.000Z","uid":91182,"like":13,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"c00a792a3a0ddc8666983d59ca776bdf623addaf","tid":714911,"uid":91182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T04:29:45.000Z","msg":"早兩日尼日利亞贏咗冰島 令到亞軍廷有機會出到線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n昨晚日耳曼又喺打少個嘅情況之下打贏瑞典 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隨時會令到唔少大牌嘅國家隊喺淘汰賽走埋同一邊 甚至乎16強已經要互相對撼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 個人意見同估計 同埋好想小花分組賽出局 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nA組  估計 首名 俄羅斯  次名 烏龜 （其實呢組首次名都係是撚但就得)<br />\nB組  估計 首名 西班牙  次名 C朗朋友隊<br />\nC組  估計 首名 法國  次名 丹麥<br />\nD組  估計 首名 格仔  次名 亞軍廷<br />\nE組  估計 首名 巴西  次名 是撚但<br />\nF組  估計 首名 墨西哥  次名 日耳曼<br />\nG組  估計 首名 比利時  次名 英撚<br />\nH組  估計 首名 是撚但  次名 是撚但<br />\n<br />\n16強嘅對賽 就可能係 （分左右邊）：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/122112_fd4c8e59b8a7add298869bd9fef2417c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F122112_fd4c8e59b8a7add298869bd9fef2417c.JPG&h=bb0e7e3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就會見到16強已經有普巴同小花鬥散步 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋巴西德國7:1復仇戰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算過到16強 你都會見到同一邊仲有葡萄牙同比利時  十分難打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n相反第二邊廂 西班牙最大嘅對手會係克羅地亞<br />\n而英格蘭就會係墨西哥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔係話克羅地亞同墨西哥唔勁 <br />\n只不過另一邊實在太多賽前嘅冠軍熱門  <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n實在精彩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"374f08a59345e0d4c029e285c6c12f0b84ce8dab","tid":714911,"uid":85819,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T04:33:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"74e2c50f3f473633c2e24d2d8a74a764c1fa2ce4","tid":714911,"uid":4496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T04:34:17.000Z","msg":"就咁睇<br />\n<br />\nB組首名可以直入決賽<br />\n西班牙/提子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47471173b88caaff48d869a5eb015d883685ba42","tid":714911,"uid":91182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"374f08a59345e0d4c029e285c6c12f0b84ce8dab","tid":714911,"uid":85819,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T04:33:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T04:35:47.000Z","msg":"不嬲都冇對英撚有任何期望 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7de39a8596e081c1cd80674ff7133c2856b065c5","tid":714911,"uid":149494,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"74e2c50f3f473633c2e24d2d8a74a764c1fa2ce4","tid":714911,"uid":4496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T04:34:17.000Z","msg":"就咁睇<br />\n<br />\nB組首名可以直入決賽<br />\n西班牙/提子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T04:40:21.000Z","msg":"提子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 哪來的自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e4f5d3956482cb1e5647d22dba58dc3129f14c","tid":714911,"uid":44083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06